{
  "text": "Spectroscopy studies Overall the same major functional groups (O-H, =C-H, C=O, N-H, N-O and C-N) were found at the surface of the membranes of Gram-negative and Grampositive bacteria, these are typical binding groups reported to be involved in the binding of dyes and metals [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
